@desc Delete a pending review for a pull request
@required {owner: str # The account owner of the repository. The name is not case sensitive., repo: str # The name of the repository. The name is not case sensitive., pull_number: int # The number that identifies the pull request., review_id: int # The unique identifier of the review.}
